<item>
            <title>[LU-19282] Don&apos;t publish obd_statfs_info in lustre_user.h</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19282</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Working on &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19066&quot; title=&quot;FLR2: identify rack/PSU failure domains for servers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19066&quot;&gt;LU-19066&lt;/a&gt; is was noticed we publish obd_statfs_info in lustre_user.h.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This structure is onyl used internally by the MDS to pass data between modules so it should not be part of the user API.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Move this structure definition to odb_support.h instead.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
